<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>英雄：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a national hero
民族英雄</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>男主角；男主人公：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The hero of this novel is a poor peasant.
这部小说的男主人公是一位贫苦的农民。</p></div>

